lead_paragraph: A casino company that agreed to Donald Trump's demand to remove his name from its now-closed Trump Plaza is refusing to strip the name from its lone remaining casino, the struggling Trump Taj Mahal.

headline.main: Casino Resisting Donald Trump's Bid to Remove Name
